              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The scattering material is placed in layers inside an",
                "inverted Cd cup in such a way that neutrons moving",
                "upwards from the graphite of a thermal column are",
                "scattered backwards from the scatterer and strike an",
                "In foil protected by Cd from a direct beam. The",
                "scattering cross section of a material is determined",
                "by comparing its back-scattering to that of graphite."
              ]
            }
          ],
